(Six officers from the patrol station
were killed.)

59
00:05:40,310 --> 00:05:41,360
(Inspector Cheng Mingxuan)

60
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,750
(also died in the line of duty.)

61
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,630
(What's worrying is)

62
00:05:45,830 --> 00:05:48,190
