95
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,800
I didn't expect you

96
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:12,000
to say this to me.

97
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,190
What you thought was a first meeting

98
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:24,600
was actually something
I had planned for a long time.

99
00:08:37,420 --> 00:08:43,300
(Cheng Feng,
Chief Inspector of Patrol Station)

100
00:09:11,790 --> 00:09:13,320
(You didn't die?)

101
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:35,840
Officer,

102
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,480
