(Arrest Warrant)

104
00:09:49,620 --> 00:09:51,320
I'm Cheng Feng, Chief Inspector
of the Patrol Station.

105
00:09:52,390 --> 00:09:53,630
I received a tip-off

106
00:09:54,150 --> 00:09:55,600
