in the venue.

107
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:58,080
Please cooperate with us
in the investigation.

108
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,750
- Opium?
- This is a serious matter.

109
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:01,750
This is not something to mess with.

110
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:04,000
I'm Yan Liang, the president

111
00:10:04,390 --> 00:10:05,510
