121
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,280
I was forced.

122
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:38,270
I swear I won't touch it again, President.

123
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,550
Please forgive me.

124
00:10:55,790 --> 00:10:56,630
President Yan,

125
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,720
